{"tid":372022,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"得罪講句，澳門人係香港人既榜樣!","createTime":"2017-08-24T05:15:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-24T05:46:23.000Z","uid":77642,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"daf73b462f9c56b6feb56005e0eb5bb7590fac55","tid":372022,"uid":77642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T05:15:37.000Z","msg":"天災既野人大家無人想，<br />\n但澳門人面對天災，積極求變，值得學習<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n1.擔佔先機領取可用物資<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2.睇準機遇，以$100飯盒同$150水賺得最大利益<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n3.態度務實，天災過後並無將責任推諉於政府，努力重建<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n4.隨遇而安，死人塌樓視作等閒，泰山崩於前而色不變，<br />\n唔似香港人咁成人指罵政府，不識禮數，態度輈張跋扈，<br />\n死人、停電、停水仍然態度積極<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n相反，香港人，比人捉個書店老闆番祖國又嘈又遊行，<br />\n立廿三條又遊行，國民教育又遊行，DQ又遊行，<br />\n官商勾結又嘈，政府無效率又嘈，毫不務實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呢D野澳門都一早有啦，但澳門人沉著面對，<br />\n今次事件睇得出澳門人真係高香港人幾班<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acd5ada9392c92b7955b4e6e26e26a4ee06df55a","tid":372022,"uid":6294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T05:35:28.000Z","msg":"的士佬為左保持災後經濟穩定<br />\n仲推岀左$800單程車費套餐<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59a859e13c82656cde734a6d85520e5d959e3a36","tid":372022,"uid":57835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T05:37:48.000Z","msg":"我幾時都話澳門人叻仔黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bcd115593a79daf5803ea9fd5d9755b212cf122","tid":372022,"uid":77642,"like"